item.description:
invalid: <p>
This filter is one of a few which are applied very early on during the bootstrap process of WordPress Multisite, before the current site has been determined.
</p>
<p>
This filter fires before plugins are loaded, but it can be used within a custom <code>wp-content/sunrise.php</code> file. For example:
</p>
<pre class="wiki">add_filter( 'pre_get_site_by_path', function( $site, $domain, $path, $segments, $paths ) {
	return WP_Site::get_instance( rand( 1, 10 ) );
}, 10, 5 );
</pre>
